==== 广东华南虎（广东东莞银行） ====
本次总决赛为[[广东宏远篮球俱乐部|广东东莞银行]]第十五次获得CBA总决赛参赛资格，而在过往十四次总决赛中，广东队合共获得九次CBA总冠军<ref name=final_records>{{Cite news|author=范佳元|title=中职篮总决赛 期待更多精彩|url=http://paper.people.com.cn/rmrb/html/2020-08/10/nw.D110000renmrb_20200810_1-15.htm|date=2020-08-10|newspaper=《[[人民日报|人民日报]]》|pages=15|access-date=2020-08-11|archive-date=2021-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210131160415/http://paper.people.com.cn/rmrb/html/2020-08/10/nw.D110000renmrb_20200810_1-15.htm}}</ref>。在本赛季开始前，广东队便明确其在该赛季的目标为拿下队史第十个CBA总冠军<ref>{{Cite news|author=李元春|title=三英战广东 书豪刮旋风|url=http://paper.xinmin.cn/html/xmwb/2019-11-01/19/47463.html|date=2019-11-01|newspaper=《[[新民晚报|新民晚报]]》|pages=19|access-date=2020-08-11|archive-date=2021-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208080456/http://paper.xinmin.cn/html/xmwb/2019-11-01/19/47463.html}}</ref>。

本季常规赛中，广东队提早七轮获得常规赛冠军<ref>{{Cite news|author=彭博|title=22连胜！|url=http://epaper.southcn.com/nfdaily/html/2020-07/09/content_7892563.htm|date=2020-07-09|newspaper=《[[南方日报|南方日报]]》|pages=A08|access-date=2020-07-13|archive-date=2020-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200712183051/http://epaper.southcn.com/nfdaily/html/2020-07/09/content_7892563.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，最终取得44胜2负的成绩<ref name=Southern_Tigers_regular>{{Cite news|author=汪雅云|title=广东队季后赛对手会是谁？|url=http://epaper.oeeee.com/epaper/A/html/2020-07/27/content_21710.htm|date=2020-07-27|newspaper=《[[南方都市报|南方都市报]]》|pages=A15|access-date=2020-08-11|archive-date=2021-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210202071724/http://epaper.oeeee.com/epaper/A/html/2020-07/27/content_21710.htm}}</ref>。广东队在该季常规赛的胜率为95.7%，乃队史最佳<ref>{{Cite news|author=吴文俊|title=易建联当选MVP|url=http://epaper.zhoudaosh.com/html/2020-07/31/content_958471.html|date=2020-07-31|newspaper=《[[新闻晨报|新闻晨报]]》|pages=16|access-date=2020-08-11|archive-date=2020-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200908114617/http://epaper.zhoudaosh.com/html/2020-07/31/content_958471.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>；输球场次为2场，与[[2009-10年中国男子篮球职业联赛|2009-10赛季常规赛]]并列队史最少<ref name=Southern_Tigers_regular/>。另外，该队亦在本季常规赛中获得29连胜<ref name=round_1>{{Cite news|author=郝浩宇|title=坐镇上半区，广东队有挑战|url=http://ep.ycwb.com/epaper/ycwb/html/2020-07/28/content_122_294480.htm|date=2020-07-28|newspaper=《[[羊城晚报|羊城晚报]]》|pages=A10|access-date=2020-08-11|archive-date=2021-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210131170952/http://ep.ycwb.com/epaper/ycwb/html/2020-07/28/content_122_294480.htm}}</ref>，刷新了其在[[2014-15年中国男子篮球职业联赛|2014-15赛季常规赛]]创造的CBA常规赛单赛季最长连胜记录（26场）<ref>{{Cite news|author=王晨征|title=回首常规赛，考验不常规|url=https://epaper.timedg.com/html/2020-07/28/content_1621952.htm|date=2020-07-28|newspaper=《东莞日报》|pages=A11|access-date=2020-08-11|archive-date=2021-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206101049/https://epaper.timedg.com/html/2020-07/28/content_1621952.htm}}</ref>。

[[2020年CBA季后赛|本季季后赛]]中，广东东莞银行在第一轮被轮空<ref name=round_1/>，第二轮则是与[[青岛国信双星雄鹰篮球俱乐部|青岛国信双星]]对阵，最终以110比88击败对手，进入上半区半决赛<ref>{{Cite news|author=李翔|title=广东北京会师半决赛|url=http://epaper.lnd.com.cn/lnrbepaper/pc/con/202008/03/content_80214.html|date=2020-08-03|newspaper=《[[辽宁日报|辽宁日报]]》|pages=08|access-date=2020-08-11|archive-date=2021-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210131103348/http://epaper.lnd.com.cn/lnrbepaper/pc/con/202008/03/content_80214.html}}</ref>。而在半决赛中，广东东莞银行先在第一场以111比109险胜[[北京鸭首钢篮球俱乐部|北京首钢]]<ref>{{Cite news|author=冯爱军|title=阿联缺阵 宏远加时险胜北京首钢|url=http://epaper.xxsb.com/html/content/2020-08/05/content_826611.html|date=2020-08-05|newspaper=《[[信息时报|信息时报]]》|pages=A09|access-date=2020-08-11|archive-date=2021-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210131061600/http://epaper.xxsb.com/html/content/2020-08/05/content_826611.html}}</ref>，北京队在第二场以90比86追平大比分<ref>{{Cite news|author=苏娅辉|title=林书豪率北京队扳回一城|url=http://epaper.jwb.com.cn/jwb/html/2020-08/07/content_15362_3099872.htm|date=2020-08-07|newspaper=《[[今晚报|今晚报]]》|pages=10|access-date=2020-08-11|archive-date=2021-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210131110600/http://epaper.jwb.com.cn/jwb/html/2020-08/07/content_15362_3099872.htm}}</ref>，广东队最终在第三场以88比85战胜北京，从而以2比1的大比分获得本赛季总决赛参赛资格<ref name=overview_1/>。

